@page "/"

<PageTitle>NethereumDapp</PageTitle>

<h1>NethereumDapp</h1>

<p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 2rem;">A complete dApp development environment powered by <strong>Nethereum</strong> and <strong>.NET Aspire</strong>.</p>

<div class="card">
    <h2 class="card-title">Getting Started</h2>
    <ul class="info-list">
        <li>
            <span class="info-label">Token Interaction</span>
            <a href="/token">Connect your wallet, switch to the DevChain network, deploy &amp; interact with tokens</a>
        </li>
        <li>
            <span class="info-label">Explorer</span>
            <span>Browse blocks, transactions, and decoded contract calls in the Aspire dashboard</span>
        </li>
        <li>
            <span class="info-label">Contracts</span>
            <span>Edit Solidity in <code>contracts/src/</code>, rebuild with <code>forge build</code>, regenerate C#</span>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2 class="card-title">Architecture</h2>
    <table class="arch-table">
        <thead>
            <tr><th>Service</th><th>Description</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr><td>DevChain</td><td>Local Ethereum node with JSON-RPC, EIP-1559, debug tracing</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Indexer</td><td>Indexes blocks, transactions, token transfers into PostgreSQL</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Explorer</td><td>Blazor blockchain explorer with contract interaction</td></tr>
            <tr><td>WebApp</td><td>This dApp UI with EIP-6963 wallet integration</td></tr>
            <tr><td>LoadGenerator</td><td>Generates test transactions for load testing</td></tr>
            <tr><td>ContractServices</td><td>Generated C# typed contract access from Solidity ABI</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
